name: Vanguard Canadian Aggregate Bond Index ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of Vanguard Canadian Aggregate Bond Index ETF the ETF is to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Bloomberg Global Aggregate Canadian Float Adjusted Bond Index the Index or the Benchmark. To achieve investment objective the fund seeks to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of a broad Canadianbond index. Currently, this Vanguard ETF seeks to track the Bloomberg Global Aggregate Canadian Float Adjusted Bond Index (orany successor thereto). It invests primarily in public, investment-grade fixed income securities issued in Canada.
